snippet.title: Seven Nights Ghost - Full Game Longplay Walkthrough | 4K | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Seven Nights Ghost - Psychological horror game | Full Game Longplay Walkthrough | 4K60fps | No Commentary

Welcome to i Scream Games Network!

Join me, as I move into the company housing in a provincial area by himself for one week for work. The company housing, which is scheduled to be demolished in seven days, is actually a house that has a bad reputation for being haunted. It will just be 7 days, however the bizarre sightings goes beyond any logical mind can comprehend, except to accept that I am not alone. Experiencing a mysterious life for seven days together, full of curses and warmth.
